Dj Powerade, Noise CasinoÂ , Juana ValeriaÂ , SEPBTTÂ , Dj Rolo, Presea
information:
On October 12th, Artik Freiburg opens its doors again for a club night curated by RUTA, featuring two distinct floors: club and perreo.

At the club floor, Dj Powerade from Impuls Crew, fresh off his recent EP Range of Motion, will soundtrack the night with a careful selection of breaks, jersey club, dembow, and UK bass. Noise Casino, following his latest release on Artficio, Pa, brings his signature style: bass-heavy broken rhythms, and fast-paced percussion. Rounding up the lineup, Juana Valeria will deliver a set of techno, breaks and bass, with a touch of Latin underground.

Also the perreo floor is back. This time Presea, Dj Rolo and Sepbtt will be playing everything between old school and new school Reggaeton, Dembow, Neo Perreo, Latin Club, and what not.â€¨
Join us on October 12th for this intersection of sounds, full of contrasts, togetherness, and boundless energy.
